Crazy, Stupid, Love.;;78;;79;;PG-13;;Cal Weaver (Steve Carell) is living the American dream. He has a good job, a beautiful house, great children and a beautiful wife, named Emily (Julianne Moore). Cal's seemingly perfect life unravels, however, when he learns that Emily has been unfaithful and wants a divorce. Over 40 and suddenly single, Cal is adrift in the fickle world of dating. Enter, Jacob Palmer (Ryan Gosling), a self-styled player who takes Cal under his wing and teaches him how to be a hit with the ladies.;;Comedy,Romance;;Glenn Ficarra,John Requa;;2011;;Steve Carell,Ryan Gosling,Julianne Moore,Emma Stone,Analeigh Tipton,Jonah Bobo,Joey King,Marisa Tomei,Beth Littleford,John Carroll Lynch,Kevin Bacon,Liza Lapira,Josh Groban,Mekia Cox,Julianna Guill,Zayne Emory;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crazy_stupid_love_2011